message.body: The Easter box came yesterday, thanks mom!! The bag is great and I'll definitely use the yoga clothes.
I talked with the lady who made the bag...she was really sweet. Have fun with your class today
￼￼There are 2 woodpeckers building a nest in our tree! Dad and I are going car shopping again today. I'll keep you posted.
Yeah! Congratulations ! You're a great teacher I'm sure! Very proud of you
